Package: tspCity
Type: Package
Title: Travel Tools: TSP Routing, Hotel Search, and City Weather Visualization on Interactive Maps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Anastasiia",
      family = "Petrus",
      email = "Anastasiia.Petrus@campus.lmu.de",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A user-friendly R package for travel planning and interactive visualization. 
    Provides functions to solve and visualize the Traveling Salesman Problem (TSP) for cities or coordinate points 
    (with automatic geocoding), find hotels using OpenStreetMap data, and display current weather with emojis on interactive maps. 
    Ideal for quick demonstrations, teaching, and exploratory travel data analysis.
